                    | was a dead black, and the stars had ceased to twinkle.
                p.text-content By the same illusion which lifts the horizon of the sea to the level of the
                    | spectator on a hillside, the sable cloud beneath was dished out, and the car seemed
                    | to float in the middle of an immense dark sphere, whose upper half was strewn with silver.
